1
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:55,220
=Episode 1=
=A Sudden Reunion=

2
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:01,080
If you walk out now,

3
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,880
we're done.

4
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:07,880
Fine.

5
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:13,080
I'll respect your choice.

6
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:40,820
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

7
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:42,660
(Suga Love)

8
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:46,500
(Suga Love)

9
00:02:09,040 --> 00:02:11,120
This outfit looks awful.

10
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:14,120
But since I get to match with you,

11
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,520
I actually think it looks great.

12
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:17,040
We can't choose our background,

13
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,880
but I'll protect you.

14
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,680
Ding Daang and Chen Aming

15
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,960
will stay together forever.

16
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:27,690
Who gave you the right to decide for me?

17
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,720
- But...
- Ding Daang.

18
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,000
I owe you more than I can repay.

19
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:35,360
I told you, I just can't pay it back.

20
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:38,240
If you're that kindhearted,
why not adopt a dog instead?

21
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:44,800
♪If this is as far as we can go♪

22
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:50,290
♪It must be because of fate♪

23
00:02:50,530 --> 00:02:57,520
♪It's not something I can keep
just because I want to♪

24
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:02,170
♪Still, I truly want to thank you♪

25
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:04,040
(Is that you, Aming?)

26
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,920
(You really came back.)

27
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,730
(If losing yourself)

28
00:03:14,230 --> 00:03:15,890
(is the price for forgetting the past,)

29
00:03:17,170 --> 00:03:18,890
(how am I supposed to save you?)

30
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,340
(My dear Aming.)

31
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:37,080
Single folks,

32
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,120
let's meet up for drinks.

33
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:40,240
Hi everyone, I'm your relationship coach,

34
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,280
Zhou Haoran.

35
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,720
Let me introduce my stunning partner,

36
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,880
Miss Gu Ruomai.

37
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:44,880
Hello everyone,

38
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,040
I'm Maimai.

39
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:47,000
Welcome, everyone,

40
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,480
to Keep Love's offline singles party

41
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:51,000
in Mancheng.

42
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,000
Keep Love is

43
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,040
a brand-new dating app, now live,

44
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,760
packed with tons of romance features,

45
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:58,400
including an exclusive
real-time heartbeat index.

46
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:00,240
With an exclusive smartwatch accessory,

47
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,920
your feelings become visible.

48
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:05,240
Keep Love, your personal love guardian.

49
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,920
So everyone, please follow us

50
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:08,080
and check out more

51
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,200
from today's singles party.

52
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,120
Aming.

53
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,880
It's really you.

54
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:09,200
Ding...

55
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,520
Daang.

56
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,280
My name's Ding Daang.

57
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,640
Like the sound

58
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:31,040
from a spoon falling into a bowl.

59
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,120
Such a lovely name.

60
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,840
I remember you.

61
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,520
Really?

62
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,280
My...

63
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,640
mom works for your family as a maid.

64
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,320
Sister Bi.

65
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,720
Long time no see.

66
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,080
You're back in Mancheng.

67
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:04,880
Is that a problem?

68
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,160
Let's... reintroduce ourselves.

69
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,120
I go by

70
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:17,880
Yu Kun now.

71
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,480
Yu... Kun.

72
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:29,680
President Yu.

73
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,600
Miss Ding.

74
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,840
Miss Ding.

75
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,240
Goodbye.

76
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,320
(No,)

77
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,840
(you're not Yu Kun.)

78
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,280
Chen Aming!

79
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:00,200
In the future you planned,

80
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:02,280
was I never part of it?

81
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:05,640
Didn't we agree to
work through this together?

82
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,800
Together?

83
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:19,000
Haven't I been trying hard enough?

84
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,640
Tell me,

85
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,600
what more do you want me to do?

86
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,200
Ding Daang.

87
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:30,360
Being with you is exhausting.

88
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:33,520
I've done everything I could.

89
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,480
Please, just let me go.

90
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,600
I'm begging you, set me free.

91
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,880
I'm begging you.

92
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:41,040
I'm begging you.

93
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,440
What happened?

94
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,910
You...

95
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,560
What happened to you?

96
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:51,600
Are you dealing with something tough?

97
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,280
Talk to me, I can help you.

98
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:55,120
Aming, I can help you.

99
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,920
Wow, you're really caring.

100
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:06,280
If you're that kindhearted,
why not adopt a dog instead?

101
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,320
Aming.

102
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,520
Come back.

103
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,760
Come back, please.

104
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:27,000
It really is Chen Aming.

105
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,640
But why did he change his name?

106
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:34,080
He's not quite how you remember him, right?

107
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,360
Still the same.

108
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:43,440
Don't fall for his tricks again.

109
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:49,240
That Zhou Haoran sure talks a lot.

110
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,520
I can ask around.

111
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,440
You're drunk.

112
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,400
Let me send you home.

113
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,000
Send me home?

114
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,000
And who exactly are you to me?

115
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:36,160
Your bestie's busy chatting
with Mr. Zhou.

116
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,800
She can't look after you right now.

117
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,480
Tell me,

118
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:05,960
should I call you Aming…

119
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,760
or Yu Kun instead?

120
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,800
And what about me?

121
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,640
Should I be calling you

122
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:16,800
Miss Ding

123
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:17,720
or...

124
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,400
Mrs. Hu?

125
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,960
Got you, huh.

126
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,240
Still pretending.

127
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:28,600
You've already dug up all the details.

128
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:32,720
I think you should call me,

129
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,200
First Love.

130
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,600
Well, Miss First Love,

131
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:41,400
you're getting engaged in just two days.

132
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,160
Still not done having fun?

133
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,680
Do you even dare?

134
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,680
Completely useless.

135
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,960
You

136
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,760
haven't changed at all.

137
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:34,320
Hand me the drink.

138
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:36,800
Come on.

139
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,240
That's all you can handle.

140
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,320
And you're drinking out?

141
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,200
Give me the drink.

142
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:48,960
No way.

143
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:49,840
You've had enough.

144
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,160
Water.

145
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,480
Stop bossing me around.

146
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:54,880
Fine.

147
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,240
I won't bother you.

148
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,640
Call your fiancé.

149
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:01,120
Ask him

150
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,330
to take you home.

151
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,480
Cut the chatter.

152
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,000
Just tell me,

153
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,280
do you dare to play?

154
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:09,640
Alright.

155
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,960
Your place or mine?

156
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,240
Actually,

157
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:19,160
I'm curious about you two's place.

158
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,280
What's it like?

159
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,520
Interesting.

160
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,040
Chen Aming.

161
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:45,040
Why did you come back?

162
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:53,000
You made that choice back then.

163
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,440
You should've disappeared for good.

164
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,680
Why show up out of nowhere now?

165
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,440
Why come back just to mess with my life?

166
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,200
Fine.

167
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:08,600
I'm sorry.

168
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,680
I should go.

169
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:22,800
Miss Ding.

170
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,200
What exactly do you want from me?

171
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,760
The past

172
00:13:33,020 --> 00:13:34,680
isn't something I can forget at will.

173
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,400
Didn't you always say

174
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,800
that you owed me too much?

175
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:41,160
Alright then.

176
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,800
You'll have to make up all the pain

177
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,400
I went through back then.

178
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,080
Fine.

179
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,480
How do you want me to make it up to you?

180
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:12,720
If you truly feel guilty about it,

181
00:14:13,140 --> 00:14:14,380
stay with me for one more week.

182
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,400
What do you think?

183
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,560
And after that?

184
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,360
After that,

185
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,250
we go our separate ways.

186
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,440
Deal?

187
00:14:58,520 --> 00:14:59,400
(Aming,)

188
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:00,800
(wait for me.)

189
00:15:07,880 --> 00:15:08,960
Have you made up your mind?

190
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,680
You said you'd make it up to me.

191
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:15,520
Ruomai.

192
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:17,960
Where's Ding Daang?

193
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,040
President Hu.

194
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,720
I'm her fiancé.

195
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:23,100
(Hu Yitong)
Then who am I?

196
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,280
Good question.

197
00:15:49,410 --> 00:15:56,410
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

198
00:16:00,810 --> 00:16:08,170
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

199
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:14,560
♪They say♪

200
00:16:14,970 --> 00:16:23,350
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

201
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:26,850
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

202
00:16:27,070 --> 00:16:33,020
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

203
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:40,160
♪I've already lost you♪

204
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:45,640
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

205
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:51,890
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

206
00:16:51,890 --> 00:16:56,670
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

207
00:16:57,780 --> 00:17:01,810
♪The past will always pass♪

208
00:17:02,140 --> 00:17:09,720
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

209
00:17:10,190 --> 00:17:13,440
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

210
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:19,650
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

211
00:17:22,110 --> 00:17:25,640
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

212
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:31,900
♪But sadly, it's not you♪
